The paper discusses the design of AI agents using deep reinforcement learning, which falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural networks (cs.NE). The use of sensory inputs and control policies also suggests computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO) as potential categories.
